{Speech 2}{}{Listen, I'm just having a drink. Leave me be.@@I don't talk to strangers. It ain't healthy to be in this bar.@@I've heard about you. Hell, but did you come to the right place?@@Looking for trouble? Go see Merk.@@Don't talk to me! I don't want to get beaten up.@@Damn cheap whiskey! You know, they serve liquor here.@@Shit! I didn't mean to spill whiskey on you. Let me wipe it off. Sorry, sorry.@@They shouldn't do that. Someday, stranger, I'll get a rifle and shoot 'em all.@@You haven't heard anything about...@@So I says to him, "Listen", I says...@@Try the fried rat. It's the best around.@@Hey! Is that your sign?@@Shit! Did you see that?@@I feel sick.@@Hey, mix up one of those!@@I drank a Red-a-Waster in one go...}
